    • Constructor Detail

      • Extreme3DPro

        public Extreme3DPro(int channel,
                    double deadbandXY,
                    double deadbandZ)
        Initializes a Joystick on a specific channel, mapping the buttons. The Joystick will never return a value in between +/- the deadband value.
        Parameters:
        channel - the channel the Joystick is plugged into
        deadbandXY - the value of the deadband on x and y axes, from 0 to 1
        deadbandZ - the value of the deadband on z axis, from 0 to 1
